{"tid":1536963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該你地班暴徒唔好再攪事 再圍警署你就後果自負","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T20:12:36.000Z","uid":188828,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f976467e09bba59d1e81315ca0fcb5c3f3761b","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我標題撚<br />\n我第一句係同狗講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">第二句係同各位手足講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位 我地已經連續幾日出咗黎<br />\n831 91 92 93 我都出晒<br />\n講真 我地要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">停一停</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢幾日太多事發生</strong></span></span><br />\n淨係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">831太子單野已經係大件事過核爆</span></span><br />\n到宜家仲未知有冇人失蹤<br />\n<br />\n你宜家呢幾日加上大圍捕同圍狗屋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">每日都太多新聞</span></span><br />\n我記得之前手足話如果活動太密<br />\n舊新聞好容易比新既新聞遮蓋<br />\n有冇人發現點解呢幾日冇咩文宣？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為做唔切！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n831尋人事件理應<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無限放大</strong></span></span>！！！<br />\n推到國際討論區<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>懷疑黑警殺人</strong></span></span><br />\n另外琴晚白衫男仔問咗句良心去咗邊<br />\n就俾人打到流晒血<br />\n中學白色恐怖<br />\n推信用評分制 又禁錮學生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢個都係核彈！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n今日六個黑警壓落手足頸椎令佢失去知覺<br />\n又係巴士持槍搜捕示威者<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>呢啲都係核彈！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實宜家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">對家俾晒彈藥我地</span></span><br />\n文宣手足都要時間做野<br />\n如果你日日圍狗屋又俾人拉既<br />\n只會遮蓋晒前幾日既事件<br />\n而文宣又做唔切 又對外宣傳不足！！！<br />\n<br />\n我唔係左膠和理非<br />\n只係覺得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太多彈藥唔用會好浪費！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外好想講<br />\n前線兄弟姊妹<br />\n如果發夢時你地想留<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我希望有個原因</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就係反擊打狗</strong></span></span><br />\n如果你地留但又只係set RB 等狗爭緩<br />\n上晒gear就暴走<br />\n咁不如唔好留<br />\n睇到佢呢幾日既取態<br />\n真係想拉鳩晒我地<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n你話留低反擊既 ok 可以<br />\n但如果你又講唔出留既原因 <br />\n我真係唔知辛辛苦苦整鐵馬企係度對峙有乜幫助<br />\n<br />\n其實真係講到口水都乾<br />\n但我仲有野想講<br />\n次次一聽到有狗就9秒9走人<br />\n明明前一秒好多人<br />\n下一秒已經跑晒仲要係咁推推推<br />\n講咗<span style=\"color: red;\">我地人多勢眾一人一腳都踩死佢地啦驚閪咩</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>究竟你地想唔想贏？</strong></span><br />\n日日扮可憐俾人打跪地求饒只會俾人打得仲甘<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你一日唔還手你一日都係俾人㩒住黎毒打</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係冇外國有義務幫我地<br />\n成日講烏克蘭革命好感動<br />\n人地死咗幾多人記唔記得<br />\n人地幾多被失蹤記唔記得<br />\n人地用火用生命做賭注又記唔記得<br />\n<br />\n宜家有疑似狗扮我地玩火就即刻話火魔法既係鬼<br />\n你地嘔唔嘔心？<br />\n火係應該人人都要學！<br />\n老實講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你諗下 你係班狗 <br />\n對住俾人打淨係識求饒<br />\n對住狗只係識dum低手足自己狂奔<br />\n淨係識自己走先<br />\n你驚唔驚佢地？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地幾撚賤都好<br />\n有幾樣野我地要學<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一團結</span></span><br />\n佢地無限包庇同僚 乜都當睇唔到<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第二 唔放棄手足</span></span><br />\n有狗落單被打都好 佢地一定有人黎救<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三 面向敵人</span></span><br />\n唔會俾人搞後面<br />\n<br />\n我講完 <br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">心態同行動上願意升級未</span></span><br />\n最低成本既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Hit n Run !!!!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dc4b4c34af078bf13a0f4d414a83daeffe2f3096","tid":1536963,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21cb7035d6de6989b125c43bf2f26b2f16a93a29","tid":1536963,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:28:12.000Z","msg":"我同意"},{"pid":"bd642198234ea92a015bf9ce5b5951e1ad530bf8","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyW7z5J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyW7z5J.png&h=2626b3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEhbhi4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEhbhi4.png&h=580a1c11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vv3FaD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvv3FaD4.png&h=c109b0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWHeZxq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWHeZxq.png&h=ba9e5446&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a11ff039fd9cd2743b1a2021e7fd39e245b424d1","tid":1536963,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins>香港人一定要知！</ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"010cedb07608a7cbb813bfcc658100e1887eebc4","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:28:35.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"672021cfc2cbc18f672cefe3a68fd60079cd315f","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:28:45.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f24005f760f0b7d56f868b97778828362de28ae3","tid":1536963,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:28:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c1498f7753a9ef6e6e7a00456d654bb9338e873","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"b8d0458541cd86d6660117ac389ae380943d6b23","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:29:09.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"f8e11d8aa9c66aa9c315a4d205ddc7a6885cc1b3","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:29:20.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"2bf9a616f66beda4b592ba93fb8b1d9e72254c2c","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:29:32.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b601c46f6c24ce248b00221343d88f5a9718dc50","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:29:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"267d9424fa00cade2b08b9363a0def07929ce724","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f7e2228bfe2b6ca4ae1794491c56814ccdd3740d","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:30:07.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"927d880beee6fc8be56e0bccb4a5fb70fcb182f3","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:30:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4b193860ed5da101d14e20131b9a231b64c3ddd4","tid":1536963,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"借位一推<br />\n快閃既勇武係唔洗代價<br />\n而且少人就成事，大家諗下一個廢老咁慢手腳都可以清晒連儂牆<br />\n對家打埋啲陰陰濕濕既招，我地都可以陰陰濕濕快閃一啲有價值既地方<br />\n重點：非狗屋　快閃　十八區都有既時候　啲狗跑得去邊？<br />\n2個人一個地方 36個人都夠"},{"pid":"912d88ffcf7fb0bd000146188854304bdcb19b29","tid":1536963,"uid":283504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f893b3aafa47b2f746595ced681aba991f1a5b","tid":1536963,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:30:37.000Z","msg":"凡係標題黨都要屌<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<strong>907 機場壓測<br />\n908 人權集會<br />\n</strong><br />\n612 721 811 831<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">核心</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">價值</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Bingo Sheet</span></strong></ins><br />\n全民大批鬥<br />\n<br />\n市民鬥黑警<br />\n藍絲鬥黃絲<br />\n窮人鬥富人<br />\n教師鬥學生<br />\n抗爭者鬥記者<br />\n<br />\n<em>根本全部都係香港人<br />\n不分化 不割𥱊</em><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"f3461f938ea26b11b36025653bf7f46162624d3c","tid":1536963,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"362df8bbfbd89c995a7aa5ea86f0af74a95c58fc","tid":1536963,"uid":17381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72e0046c8fa66349d7154e406f9a7bf42a3353c","tid":1536963,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1f976467e09bba59d1e81315ca0fcb5c3f3761b","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我標題撚<br />\n我第一句係同狗講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">第二句係同各位手足講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位 我地已經連續幾日出咗黎<br />\n831 91 92 93 我都出晒<br />\n講真 我地要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">停一停</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢幾日太多事發生</strong></span></span><br />\n淨係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">831太子單野已經係大件事過核爆</span></span><br />\n到宜家仲未知有冇人失蹤<br />\n<br />\n你宜家呢幾日加上大圍捕同圍狗屋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">每日都太多新聞</span></span><br />\n我記得之前手足話如果活動太密<br />\n舊新聞好容易比新既新聞遮蓋<br />\n有冇人發現點解呢幾日冇咩文宣？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為做唔切！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n831尋人事件理應<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無限放大</strong></span></span>！！！<br />\n推到國際討論區<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>懷疑黑警殺人</strong></span></span><br />\n另外琴晚白衫男仔問咗句良心去咗邊<br />\n就俾人打到流晒血<br />\n中學白色恐怖<br />\n推信用評分制 又禁錮學生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢個都係核彈！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n今日六個黑警壓落手足頸椎令佢失去知覺<br />\n又係巴士持槍搜捕示威者<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>呢啲都係核彈！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實宜家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">對家俾晒彈藥我地</span></span><br />\n文宣手足都要時間做野<br />\n如果你日日圍狗屋又俾人拉既<br />\n只會遮蓋晒前幾日既事件<br />\n而文宣又做唔切 又對外宣傳不足！！！<br />\n<br />\n我唔係左膠和理非<br />\n只係覺得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">太多彈藥唔用會好浪費！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外好想講<br />\n前線兄弟姊妹<br />\n如果發夢時你地想留<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我希望有個原因</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就係反擊打狗</strong></span></span><br />\n如果你地留但又只係set RB 等狗爭緩<br />\n上晒gear就暴走<br />\n咁不如唔好留<br />\n睇到佢呢幾日既取態<br />\n真係想拉鳩晒我地<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n你話留低反擊既 ok 可以<br />\n但如果你又講唔出留既原因 <br />\n我真係唔知辛辛苦苦整鐵馬企係度對峙有乜幫助<br />\n<br />\n其實真係講到口水都乾<br />\n但我仲有野想講<br />\n次次一聽到有狗就9秒9走人<br />\n明明前一秒好多人<br />\n下一秒已經跑晒仲要係咁推推推<br />\n講咗<span style=\"color: red;\">我地人多勢眾一人一腳都踩死佢地啦驚閪咩</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>究竟你地想唔想贏？</strong></span><br />\n日日扮可憐俾人打跪地求饒只會俾人打得仲甘<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你一日唔還手你一日都係俾人㩒住黎毒打</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係冇外國有義務幫我地<br />\n成日講烏克蘭革命好感動<br />\n人地死咗幾多人記唔記得<br />\n人地幾多被失蹤記唔記得<br />\n人地用火用生命做賭注又記唔記得<br />\n<br />\n宜家有疑似狗扮我地玩火就即刻話火魔法既係鬼<br />\n你地嘔唔嘔心？<br />\n火係應該人人都要學！<br />\n老實講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你諗下 你係班狗 <br />\n對住俾人打淨係識求饒<br />\n對住狗只係識dum低手足自己狂奔<br />\n淨係識自己走先<br />\n你驚唔驚佢地？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地幾撚賤都好<br />\n有幾樣野我地要學<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一團結</span></span><br />\n佢地無限包庇同僚 乜都當睇唔到<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第二 唔放棄手足</span></span><br />\n有狗落單被打都好 佢地一定有人黎救<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三 面向敵人</span></span><br />\n唔會俾人搞後面<br />\n<br />\n我講完 <br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">心態同行動上願意升級未</span></span><br />\n最低成本既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Hit n Run !!!!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:39:04.000Z","msg":"打boss梗係要觀察下㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔日夜望住點會知boss弱點先<br />\n香城online一隻boss都勁難打"},{"pid":"c47377d79d09bb161b4db7c77a2b712d0c518d62","tid":1536963,"uid":182679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:04:04.000Z","msg":"點解無人推上熱門?"},{"pid":"af96df5dae5a788b087f9398b79ab6f788bc969d","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c47377d79d09bb161b4db7c77a2b712d0c518d62","tid":1536963,"uid":182679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:04:04.000Z","msg":"點解無人推上熱門?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:12:25.000Z","msg":"靠你了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f80f9d9e24117d0113388a4980358bea819a2b9","tid":1536963,"uid":188828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:12:36.000Z","msg":"［突發］可唔可以推到俾831太子逃亡手足睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537068</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}